## 🎓 Developer Notes

### **Code Standards**

```php
// ✅ Good: Dependency injection
public function __construct(DigiflazzService $digiflazz)
{
    $this->digiflazz = $digiflazz;
}

// ✅ Good: Database transactions
DB::beginTransaction();
try {
    // Operations
    DB::commit();
} catch (\Exception $e) {
    DB::rollBack();
    throw $e;
}

// ✅ Good: Eloquent with eager loading
Order::with(['product', 'user'])->get();

// ❌ Bad: N+1 query
foreach (Order::all() as $order) {
    echo $order->product->name; // N+1!
}
```

